data.name: Fresh LinkedIn Profile Data
data.title: Fresh LinkedIn Profile Data
data.description: Real-time LinkedIn Data. Search Employees at Scale. Get Access to Sales Navigator without cookies. Trusted by numerous AI startups around the world.
data.longDescription:
✅ Unofficial LinkedIn API for retrieving any type of LinkedIn data..

✅ Launched in 2022, and become the most **reliable & scalable** API for LinkedIn scraping.

️✅️️️ Search employees or companies in real-time, at scale, **without using any cookies**.

️✅️ **Unique Feature**: Be able to [fully automate LinkedIn Sales Navigator scraping](https://fdocs.info/tutorial/howto-search-leads) without the need for **cookies or accounts**. Capable of scraping hundreds of thousands of leads daily.

✅ **100% Refund Guarantee:** If you use up to **10% of your credits** and aren’t satisfied, we’ll give you a **full refund**—no questions asked.

✅ **Trusted worldwide** by numerous AI-related startups.

✅  **[External API Documentation](https://fdocs.info/)** for detailed instructions and reference.

✅ **Fast & Professional Support:** Contact us at [support@fdocs.info](mailto:support@fdocs.info).
